 A man is reportedly set to wed his three heavily pregnant lovers in Delta state. A Twitter user identified by her handle as @MrsZanga disclosed this in a tweet she made. This is coming after a man who also hails from Delta took the bold step by marrying two pregnant women on the same day which got social media agog. Sharing what seems to be a pre-wedding photo of the man and his prospective pregnant wife, the netizen wrote:

